Sentiment analysis in Arabic

This data set from the UCI ML repository is a collection of 2000 tweets from Arabic users classified by native Arabic experts at positive or negitive. This will be intresting because I do not speak Arabic. I will first try a simple classification scheme and see how that goes and then I will probably try a clustering analysis and see if any intresting paterns arise.
